               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Malkǝʾa kidāna mǝḥrat “Image of the Covenant of Mercy” (fols. 1va-4vb,
                     17va-18rb) (cp. Malkǝʾa gubaʾe, ʾAśmära 1974 E.C., pp. 63-73)
 II) Dǝrsāna
                     kidāna mǝḥrat “Homily for the Covenant of Mercy” (fols. 5ra-13vb)
 III)
                     Maṣḥafa kidāna mǝḥrat “Book of the Covenant of Mercy” (fols. 13vb-17va)
                     
 Additiones 1-2.</summary>
