               <provenance>ʾabeto Takla ʾƎgziʾ is mentioned as the
                     commissioner and donor of the Ms. in the supplication formulas (e.g., 4vb, 13vb) and in Additio 1. Besides names of his
                     family mambers are also mentioned, Walda Mikāʾel, Säbänä Giyorgis, Ḍädalä
                     Māryām, and Ṣäbälä Giyorgis.</provenance></history>
